Sun November 4, 2012 - Adopt-A-Highway road clean-up .
Meet at the first parking lot after crossing the covered bridge where PA 252
intersects Yellow Springs rd. in VFNHP. The cleanup starts at 11:00 am. Come
out and join the crew. Get a group together and ride to the cleanup.=A0 The=
re
will be snacks/ refreshments. The clean-up lasts about one hour. We assign
teams of two to cover each of the four sections. We walk along Yellow
Springs rd. and pick up by hand. It is a well maintained road, much loved by
cyclists. Your club keeps it clean and you can help. We have gloves, bags
and vests for everyone. If you do want to help, get back to a leader, we
need advance confirmation. So, please call or e-mail, in advance.
